{"tid":418339,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"HK Express突取消黃金周18航班 逾3,000客受阻","createTime":"2017-09-29T12:49:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T12:57:13.000Z","uid":142877,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8ea65f1fb14f33c999913a9fb9fd8a364ada2e1d","tid":418339,"uid":142877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T12:49:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170929&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57272247\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170929%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57272247&d=dY%2BwcgPoOsdsY2SB3VcuJ6NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=81e0af86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170929%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57272247&h=cf096a4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170929&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57272247</a><br />\n遊日韓注意！HK Express突取消黃金周18航班 逾3,000客受阻<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170929&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57272247\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170929%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57272247&d=dY%2BwcgPoOsdsY2SB3VcuJ6NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=81e0af86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170929%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57272247&h=cf096a4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170929&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57272247</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民航處證實，昨日下午接獲HK Express通知，突然取消18班，由10月1日至8日，往返香港與大阪、名古屋及首爾的定期航班。 (資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n10.1黃金周遊日韓HK Express（香港快運）乘客注意！民航處證實，昨日下午接獲HK Express通知，突然取消18班，由10月1日至8日，往返香港與大阪、名古屋及首爾的定期航班。民航處指，由於正值國慶日和中秋節假期，外遊人數較多，民航處高度關注事件對受影響旅客帶來的不便和影響，已即時聯絡香港快運航空了解事件，並於今早召見了航空公司管理層，要求該航空公司盡快聯絡受影響的旅客作出退款或其他安排。<br />\n<br />\n該公司管理層向民航處稱，已聯絡受影響旅客，並會提供其他航班供受影響旅客轉乘或安排退款。對於有航空公司在外遊高峰期前夕，作出如此大的航班改動，以致影響乘客眾多，當局認為情況極不理想。 至於導致今次航班取消的詳細原因，處方仍在了解中。民航處會要求香港快運航空提交詳細報告。"},{"pid":"25d0926470f0bfdec3182da16273206091b30f69","tid":418339,"uid":9694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T12:57:13.000Z","msg":"執笠先兆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}